Title: Superseven Unchained
Writer: T.J. Glenn (story), Jerry Kokich (story), Andrew Palmer (story), Scott Rhodes (screenplay), Scott Rhodes (story)
Actors: Jerry Kokich, Olivia Dunkley, Michelle Jubilee Gonzalez, Heather Bonomo
Plot: T.H.E.Y. has programmed Sandra West to become a T.H.E.Y. assassin. Can Superseven stop her from killing more agents and prevent her head from exploding like a poodle in a microwave?
